@startuml Sequence_UC18
title UC-18: Kelola Alur Persediaan

actor "Bagian Inventori" as User
participant "Halaman Alur\n(livewire/alur)" as View
participant "Alur\\Index\n(Livewire)" as Component
participant "InventoryLog Model" as LogModel
database "Database" as DB

User -> View: Membuka /alur-persediaan
View -> Component: mount()
Component -> LogModel: InventoryLog::with(['material','user','materialBatch'])->latest()->paginate()
LogModel -> DB: SELECT inventory_logs JOIN materials, users, material_batches
DB --> Component: Daftar log inventori
Component --> View: Render daftar log persediaan

== Filter Log ==
User -> View: Memilih filter material / action / tanggal
View -> Component: applyFilter($materialId, $action, $from, $to)
Component -> LogModel: InventoryLog::query()->when(...)->get()
LogModel -> DB: SELECT inventory_logs WHERE ...
DB --> Component: Filtered logs
Component --> View: Perbarui tampilan

== Lihat Detail & Navigasi ke Referensi ==
User -> View: Klik entri log
View -> Component: showDetail($logId)
Component -> LogModel: InventoryLog::findOrFail($logId)
LogModel -> DB: SELECT inventory_logs WHERE id = ?
DB --> Component: Log detail
Component --> View: Tampil detail log (aksi, jumlah, stok setelah, referensi)

User -> View: Klik tautan referensi
View -> Component: keRincian($referenceType, $referenceId)
Component -> Component: Tentukan route berdasarkan reference_type\n(expense→belanja.rincian,\nproduction→produksi.rincian,\nhitung→hitung.rincian)
Component --> View: Redirect ke halaman rincian dokumen

@enduml
